                        ][h2]Introduction[/h2][
                        
                        ][br][
                        
                        ]Hello there![
                        ][br][br][
                        ]· · ─ ‧₊˚❀༉‧₊˚. ─ · ·[
                        ][br][br][
                        
                        ]My name is Socio and I'm a big fan of coding! Welcome to my little custom template shop. Basically, I am here to make you clean and appealing templates for your shop, about me, trainer card, profile signature, or for anything else you can think of on PFQ![
                        
                        ][br][br][
                        ]· · ─ ‧₊˚❀༉‧₊˚. ─ · ·[
                        ][br][br][
                        
                        ][b]I provide two types of packages:[/b][
                        
                        ][br][br][
                        
                        ][b]Personalized templates[/b] are semi-custom designs built from my base layouts. You choose the colors, images, and style options, and I’ll adapt an existing template to your taste. They’re faster, budget-friendly, and perfect if you want something clean and functional without waiting on a full custom project.[
                        
                        ][br][br][
                        
                        ]Read the [b]Templates[/b] section for more information.[
                        
                        ][br][br][
                        
                        ][b]Custom templates[/b] are built from scratch with your vision in mind. You provide the themes, layouts, and features you’d like, and I’ll design drafts, revisions, and a final product tailored exactly to you. This option gives you full creative control, unique layouts, and long-term flexibility for expansions.[
                        
                        ][br][br][
                        
                        ]Read the [b]Customs[/b] section for more information.[
                        
                        ][br][br][
                        
                        ]The tabs to the left can be used to see prices and examples of my work. However, before you do that, please take the time to [b]read my rules[/b] first! By purchasing my services, you are consenting to these terms.[
                        
                        ][br][br][
                        ]· · ─ ‧₊˚❀༉‧₊˚. ─ · ·[
