                    ][h2]Personalized Templates[/h2][
                    
                    ][br][
                    
                    ]Personalized templates are feature-limited templates that are adjusted to your taste. They are semi-custom: you can choose from general layouts, colors, and images for the template. They are faster and cheaper to make, making it a good low budget option![
                    
                    ][br][br][
                    ]· · ─ ‧₊˚❀༉‧₊˚. ─ · ·[
                    ][br][br][
                    
                    ]Each template comes with a list of features, which are listed below. Some templates have a limit on how many sections can be included, extra will cost an additional fee. New custom sections may not qualify as an addition to these kinds of templates, depending on it complexity.[
                    
                    ][br][br][
                        
