                    ][h2]Customs[/h2][
                    
                    ][br][
                    
                    ]Custom templates are extremely personalized templates that are made to order. Instead of recieving having a template personalized for you, you describe the themes you want, colors, images, and elements. You can provide examples, whether that be pictures, drawings, or descriptions, to reference. Custom banners, layouts, and interactables such as buttons, icons, and more are completely on the table.[
                    
                    ][br][br][
                    
                    ]Another benefit of a custom template is I will send you draft versions throughout the process, to recieve your input. You can request changes during this phase to get exactly what you're looking for. After the template is complete, significant revisions can be added for a small fee.[
                    
                    ][br][br][
                    
                    ]Lastly, if you ever want new features, sections, or changes added later on with your template, you can do so for a reduced price. For example, if I create you a custom trade shop template and you decide you want a reply or signature template to go with it, you'll get a discount![
                    
                    ][br][br][
                    ]· · ─ ‧₊˚❀༉‧₊˚. ─ · ·[
                    ][br][br][
                    
                    ]A custom template includes the following features:[
                    
                    ][styleclass="centered-list"][
                    
                        ][ul][
                        
                            ][li]Specify any features or themes you'd like, including structure, elements, and visual aesthetics.[/li][
                            
                            ][li]Option to design new custom elements, assuming they can be implemented while still adhering to PFQ rules.[/li][
                            
                            ][li]2 - 3 drafts which give you the option to ask for revisions and adjustments.[/li][
                            
                            ][li]Custom interactive elements, such as animated displays, buttons, links, and more. Keep in mind that there are rules on PFQ for animated elements.[/li][
                            
                            ][li]Reduced price for templates / additions of the same theme later on (10% off).[/li][
                            
                        ][/ul][
                    
                    ][/styleclass][
                    
                    ][br][
                    
                    ]Currencies are swapped on a [b][number]5000[/number] [item="Credits"] : 5 [item="Gold"] : 1 [item="Zophan"][/b] conversion rate.[
                    
